{"tid":393388,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"15至17年 共70個學生自殺 高官子弟先死得1件","createTime":"2017-09-09T08:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T10:11:51.000Z","uid":29270,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"035599bf749f6c3a949da2c302787356799704c6","tid":393388,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T08:20:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2015-2017%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2015-2017%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%25BA%258C%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6&d=TMyYmSTQYqORmNDu9euszmMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=dd31ed9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2015-2017%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6</a><br />\n<br />\n自2015年9月新學年，共有71名學生主要因學業壓力而輕生。自2016年3月起，死亡數字開始攀升，並開始引發自殺模仿效應。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味有冇打過機或者聽過古人打仗<br />\n殺敵比率可以上到70比1，仲要人地係自殺<br />\n<br />\n咁都仲要講道德，講人性<br />\n屌你啦我恥笑你先叫有人性啦，唔笑都唔覺得自已有血性 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10fc8664a99f3a74cf0eb011778b35eb981536d5","tid":393388,"uid":29270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T08:22:22.000Z","msg":"特區教育局十幾年既教育改革，左改右改<br />\n<br />\n老師自殺，學生自殺，夾夾埋埋百幾條人命<br />\n百幾個家庭，上千個家屬，你班政府、五毛黨、道德撚賠返比佢地？<br />\n<br />\n加入暴政做官，仲話要推國民教育<br />\n就應有此報啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"628ada6c822d31f7378c014762e5a9ee31ac82fa","tid":393388,"uid":29270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T08:27:18.000Z","msg":"乜撚野道德、人性、血性<br />\n<br />\n70個學生，仲有未統計既老師，15年之前自殺既學生<br />\n前前後後上千家屬，千萬個同學同事親友<br />\n<br />\n比暴政害死，你班道德撚唔去屌鳩個政府？<br />\n你班所謂校董、校長、社會權貴，唔去譴責政府？<br />\n<br />\n你班友遲下落埋去團圓地府再繼中國夢啦你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6027bf5993f7c2a016f2f0bf058e86fa68184a6f","tid":393388,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:09:03.000Z","msg":"普通學生條命唔值錢<br />\n<br />\n高官仔女條命先值錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e316e446388443a6b937d7fcb29aa756c67de3c","tid":393388,"uid":141804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:11:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}